WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:03.086
(all)
♪ Get your spy on ♪

00:03.169 --> 00:04.754
♪ Spy on ♪

00:04.838 --> 00:07.340
♪ You're on a mission
with a Twist and Shout ♪

00:07.424 --> 00:08.758
♪ Shout! ♪

00:08.842 --> 00:11.094
♪ Kiki and Marina spy it up
to work it out ♪

00:11.177 --> 00:12.095
♪ Out! ♪

00:12.178 --> 00:13.972
♪ Bounce with our sidekick, Bo ♪

00:14.055 --> 00:15.682
♪ Gadgets on the go ♪

00:15.765 --> 00:18.101
♪ Who's the first at the scene
of the crime? ♪

00:18.184 --> 00:19.519
♪ Fresh Beats! ♪

00:19.602 --> 00:23.273
♪ Solving the mystery
every time ♪

00:23.356 --> 00:27.610
♪ Trouble's no match for
the Fresh Beat Band of Spies ♪

00:27.694 --> 00:29.446
♪ Get your hands up high ♪

00:29.529 --> 00:31.573
♪ Find a cool disguise ♪

00:31.656 --> 00:33.950
♪<i> Fresh Beat Band of Spies ♪</i>

00:34.033 --> 00:35.618
♪ Get your spy on ♪

00:36.995 --> 00:39.622
(Twist)
Ghost Of Rock.

00:39.706 --> 00:41.124
Wow, look at all
the fans here

00:41.207 --> 00:42.876
for the
Three Directions concert.

00:42.959 --> 00:45.837
Yeah. I was afraid there
might not be a big crowd.

00:45.920 --> 00:46.796
{\an3}Why?

00:46.880 --> 00:48.298
'Cause of the ghost.

00:48.381 --> 00:49.674
[ghostly mumbling]

00:49.758 --> 00:50.800
{\an3}Exactly.

00:50.884 --> 00:53.636
{\an3}[laughs]
That's just some silly story.

00:53.720 --> 00:54.596
{\an1}[laughs]

00:54.679 --> 00:55.263
[car horn honks]

00:55.346 --> 00:55.889
{\an1}Oh!
Here they come!

00:55.972 --> 00:59.768
[crowd screaming]

01:00.643 --> 01:03.313
Ah, ah, ah.
Watch the hair.

01:03.396 --> 01:05.272
Please don't fluffle the hair.

01:05.355 --> 01:07.650
{\an5}(man)
Cool!
It's Hamish!

01:07.734 --> 01:09.486
{\an3}Autographs after
the show.

01:09.569 --> 01:10.445
{\an3}Our favorite food
is clams.

01:10.528 --> 01:11.488
Long walks
in the moonlight.

01:11.571 --> 01:14.324
Come on, Curtis.

01:14.407 --> 01:16.326
I'm not going in there.

01:16.409 --> 01:18.369
That theater is haunted.

01:18.453 --> 01:19.496
[gasping]

01:19.579 --> 01:21.289
- Told ya.
- [mumbling]

01:21.372 --> 01:24.292
{\an3}[laughs]
It's not haunted.

01:24.375 --> 01:25.835
{\an3}That's just some
silly story.

01:25.919 --> 01:28.129
Oh, exactly.
It's a story.

01:28.213 --> 01:31.508
{\an3}Do we look like a band who would
sing at a haunted theater?

01:33.218 --> 01:34.344
Huh?

01:34.427 --> 01:35.345
[gasping]

01:35.428 --> 01:36.262
[screams]

01:36.346 --> 01:38.181
The hat is haunted!

01:38.264 --> 01:38.807
(all)
Whoa!

01:38.890 --> 01:40.725
Did you see that?

01:40.809 --> 01:42.685
{\an1}Huh.
That was weird.

01:42.769 --> 01:43.436
{\an1}Anyway...

01:43.520 --> 01:46.314
Scream if you want a show!

01:46.397 --> 01:48.316
[screaming]

01:48.399 --> 01:49.317
♪ Hey now ♪

01:49.400 --> 01:50.443
♪ Hey now, now ♪

01:50.527 --> 01:52.278
♪ No matter what you do ♪

01:52.362 --> 01:53.279
♪ Hey now ♪

01:53.363 --> 01:54.531
♪ Hey now, now ♪

01:54.614 --> 01:56.282
♪ I'm always there for you ♪

01:56.366 --> 01:57.283
♪ Hey now ♪

01:57.367 --> 01:58.535
♪ Hey now, now ♪

01:58.618 --> 01:59.577
♪ No matter what I do ♪

01:59.661 --> 02:00.578
♪ Hey now ♪

02:00.662 --> 02:02.914
♪ Hey now, now ♪

02:02.997 --> 02:04.332
♪ You're right there
for me, too ♪

02:04.415 --> 02:05.875
♪ Hey now ♪
Hey!

02:05.959 --> 02:07.669
Hey! I was--

02:07.752 --> 02:09.336
♪ Hey now ♪

02:09.419 --> 02:10.547
♪ Hey now, now ♪

02:10.630 --> 02:13.007
♪ I'm always there for you ♪

02:13.091 --> 02:13.383
♪ Hey now ♪

02:13.466 --> 02:16.094
[crash]

02:16.177 --> 02:17.303
♪ Hey now ♪

02:17.387 --> 02:18.721
{\an1}Whoa!

02:18.805 --> 02:19.681
That's strange.

02:19.764 --> 02:21.558
{\an3}They have some cool
new effects.

02:21.641 --> 02:22.642
How do they do that?

02:22.725 --> 02:23.226
{\an1}Yeah.

02:23.309 --> 02:25.228
How do they do that?

02:25.311 --> 02:27.480
{\an3}I'm not sure
those are effects.

02:28.731 --> 02:30.358
Whoa!

02:30.441 --> 02:32.402
Okay.
[laughs nervously]

02:32.485 --> 02:34.070
It's all under control.

02:34.153 --> 02:37.490
Everybody, let's see those hands
up as high as they can go!

02:37.574 --> 02:40.994
[screams]

02:45.874 --> 02:46.416
Huh?

02:46.499 --> 02:48.668
- Wow!
- Dude.

02:48.751 --> 02:50.378
A singing yo-yo.

02:50.461 --> 02:52.380
{\an1}I did not see that
coming.

02:52.463 --> 02:54.924
Whoa. Whoa.
Whoa!

02:55.008 --> 02:56.593
{\an1}Ooh!

02:56.676 --> 02:58.261
Mmm.
[crunch]

02:58.344 --> 03:03.308
Madison, you will not believe
who just landed in my nachos.

03:03.391 --> 03:05.518
This is definitely
not part of the show.

03:06.561 --> 03:08.187
{\an3}Ho-ho!
This is too much.

03:08.271 --> 03:09.272
I'm getting
out of here.

03:09.355 --> 03:10.315
[grunting]

03:10.398 --> 03:11.274
{\an1}Me too!

03:11.357 --> 03:12.275
[screaming]

03:12.358 --> 03:14.903
This place really is haunted.

03:14.986 --> 03:16.112
Wait for me!

03:16.195 --> 03:17.906
[crunching]

03:17.989 --> 03:19.949
Really, really haunted?

03:20.033 --> 03:22.368
{\an3}But what about
the show?

03:22.452 --> 03:26.289
{\an1}What if this place really is
really, really haunted?

03:26.372 --> 03:27.790
{\an1}For real.

03:27.874 --> 03:30.710
{\an3}I'm sure there's a
perfectly normal explanation

03:30.793 --> 03:33.963
{\an3}for all of this
not exactly normal stuff.

03:34.047 --> 03:36.633
Guys, there's nothing
to be afraid of.

03:36.716 --> 03:37.800
Nothing's going to pop out
and say, "Boo!"

03:37.884 --> 03:40.053
Or fly in and scare us.

03:40.136 --> 03:41.095
Fresh Beats!

03:41.179 --> 03:42.639
[screaming]
Reed!

03:42.722 --> 03:45.808
We have a mysteriously
mysterious mystery on our hands.

03:45.892 --> 03:48.728
Meet me at the music store,
right away!

03:48.811 --> 03:52.023
You know, I kinda did
see that one coming.

03:52.106 --> 03:54.651
{\an3}Hello?
Anybody here?

03:54.734 --> 03:56.110
Reed.

03:56.194 --> 03:57.195
Fresh Beats!

03:57.278 --> 03:58.655
[all gasp]
Reed!

03:58.738 --> 04:01.157
Weird things keep happening
at that theater.

04:01.240 --> 04:02.700
Night after eerie night,

04:02.784 --> 04:04.744
concert after creepy concert,

04:04.827 --> 04:07.163
haunting after
horrible haunting!

04:07.246 --> 04:09.374
[terrified mumbling]

04:09.457 --> 04:10.708
Take a look at this!

04:10.792 --> 04:14.879
[machines buzzing]

04:19.132 --> 04:21.469
{\an5}(Reed)
It happened at a rockin'
rock-n'-roll show.

04:21.552 --> 04:24.097
(man)
Whoo! You rock!

04:24.180 --> 04:25.223
Oh, no!

04:25.306 --> 04:27.016
- [gasping]
- What?

04:27.100 --> 04:28.309
[screams]

04:28.393 --> 04:31.104
Whoa!
That never happens!

04:31.187 --> 04:34.190
{\an5}(Reed)
It happened at the honky tonk
hoedown hootenanny.

04:34.274 --> 04:36.025
{\an1}Yee-haw!

04:36.109 --> 04:38.945
[yelling]

04:39.028 --> 04:40.655
Wow, that never happens!

04:40.738 --> 04:44.534
{\an5}(Reed)
It even happened happened
at harp-a-palooza!

04:44.617 --> 04:47.120
(man)
Bravo! Bravo!

04:47.203 --> 04:48.371
[startled screaming]

04:48.454 --> 04:50.707
[high-pitched opera singing]

04:50.790 --> 04:52.792
[string snaps]

04:52.875 --> 04:55.420
Ugh, this always happens here.

04:55.503 --> 04:57.839
{\an1}If these weird things
keep happening,

04:57.922 --> 04:59.632
the theater will have
to shut down forever.

04:59.716 --> 05:01.718
{\an3}What?

05:01.801 --> 05:04.262
{\an3}No!
We love that theater.

05:04.345 --> 05:06.180
{\an3}Everybody loves
that theater.

05:06.264 --> 05:08.141
{\an1}Everybody thinks
it's haunted.

05:08.224 --> 05:10.643
Then we'll have to prove
that it's not haunted.

05:10.727 --> 05:12.020
- Good.
- [mumbling]

05:12.103 --> 05:13.312
Or that it is haunted.

05:13.396 --> 05:14.897
- Bad.
- [mumbling]

05:14.981 --> 05:17.900
Fresh Beats, it's up to you
to save that theater!

05:17.984 --> 05:20.486
{\an1}This is a mission
for the Fresh Beat Band...

05:20.570 --> 05:22.071
[dramatic music]

05:22.155 --> 05:24.907
(all)
Of spies!

05:24.991 --> 05:26.576
♪ ♪

05:26.659 --> 05:28.244
Time to spy it up.

05:28.327 --> 05:29.495
[mumbles]

05:29.579 --> 05:32.540
[dramatic music]

05:32.623 --> 05:36.919
♪ ♪

05:37.003 --> 05:40.339
Kiki on scooter!

05:40.423 --> 05:41.049
♪ ♪

05:41.132 --> 05:45.303
Shout on hover board!

05:45.386 --> 05:46.763
Marina on...

05:48.514 --> 05:50.099
Turbo-wheeler!

05:50.183 --> 05:54.729
Twist on double pogo
to go-go!

05:54.812 --> 05:55.855
What's up, Bo?

05:55.938 --> 05:57.273
{\an1}Don't you want to ride
up front?

05:57.356 --> 05:58.232
{\an3}[mumbles]

05:58.316 --> 05:59.317
Yeah, me neither.

05:59.400 --> 06:06.407
♪ ♪

06:10.703 --> 06:11.913
Don't worry, guys.

06:11.996 --> 06:14.123
There's no such thing
as a ghost.

06:14.207 --> 06:16.417
But since Marina has the
flashlight, she should go first.

06:16.501 --> 06:20.880
Have no fear, Bo Monkey
and I will lead the way.

06:20.963 --> 06:22.590
{\an3}Check out
our sweet plan.

06:22.673 --> 06:24.133
Remind you of anything?

06:24.217 --> 06:26.302
[ghostly moaning]

06:26.385 --> 06:28.137
{\an3}You're disguised
as ghosts?

06:28.221 --> 06:30.932
{\an1}Yup. That way, if there are
any ghosts in there,

06:31.015 --> 06:33.893
then we'll blend right in
and no one will scare us.

06:33.976 --> 06:36.145
{\an1}But you don't have
any eye holes.

06:36.229 --> 06:37.146
[chuckles]

06:37.230 --> 06:38.439
Don't need any.

06:38.523 --> 06:41.484
{\an1}We got a mouth hole
for saying "ooh!"

06:41.567 --> 06:42.485
[clanging]

06:42.568 --> 06:43.778
{\an1}Okay,
maybe one eye hole.

06:43.861 --> 06:46.114
♪ ♪

06:46.197 --> 06:48.908
{\an1}Okay, everybody.
Look around,

06:48.991 --> 06:51.410
{\an1}and if you see anything
suspicious, give a--

06:51.494 --> 06:52.787
(Twist)
No!

06:54.831 --> 06:56.332
(Marina)
What? What is it, Twist?

06:56.415 --> 06:59.544
The snack bar is closed.

06:59.627 --> 07:00.962
{\an3}[mumbling]

07:02.213 --> 07:05.341
The whole theater is closed.

07:05.424 --> 07:09.178
Okay, time to use the spectral
inspector ghost detector.

07:09.262 --> 07:11.722
{\an1}This will help us locate
any ghost in no time.

07:11.806 --> 07:13.224
- [electronic beeping]
- [gasps]

07:13.307 --> 07:18.521
{\an1}Bo monkey, this means we're
actually g-g-ghosts.

07:18.604 --> 07:20.231
{\an3}[mumbling]

07:20.314 --> 07:22.316
{\an1}[laughs]
Don't worry guys.

07:22.400 --> 07:24.569
{\an1}That's just the sound of it
turning on.

07:24.652 --> 07:25.570
Phew!

07:25.653 --> 07:27.029
[electronic beeping]

07:27.113 --> 07:28.656
{\an3}Okay, team.
This theater is big.

07:28.739 --> 07:29.907
We'll need to split up

07:29.991 --> 07:30.533
{\an3}if we're going to search
the whole place.

07:33.786 --> 07:35.538
I'm not scared.

07:35.621 --> 07:37.123
Really not scared.

07:37.206 --> 07:38.541
- Super not scared.
- [squeaking]

07:38.624 --> 07:40.209
[screams]

07:40.293 --> 07:41.377
Um, who's there?

07:41.460 --> 07:44.046
Don't make me come find you!

07:44.130 --> 07:46.883
[squeaking]

07:53.472 --> 07:56.684
One, two, three!

07:56.767 --> 07:57.059
Gotcha!

07:57.143 --> 07:59.270
Huh?

07:59.353 --> 08:00.396
[squeaking]

08:00.479 --> 08:02.023
[laughs]

08:02.106 --> 08:04.775
Shout was right.
There's nothing to be afraid of.

08:04.859 --> 08:06.068
- [electronic beeping]
- [screams]

08:06.152 --> 08:06.861
Whoa!

08:06.944 --> 08:08.404
- [crash]
- [grunts]

08:08.487 --> 08:09.739
[electronic beeping]

08:09.822 --> 08:12.658
Kiki, Twist here.
Do you have any snacks?

08:12.742 --> 08:14.118
[chuckles]

08:14.202 --> 08:15.912
If there are any ghosts
around here I'll--

08:15.995 --> 08:19.123
Yah! Cha! So! La! Ti! Do!

08:19.207 --> 08:20.416
[gasps]
What's that?

08:20.499 --> 08:21.417
[rattling]

08:21.500 --> 08:22.627
Relax, Shout.

08:22.710 --> 08:25.671
It's probably just the wind.

08:25.755 --> 08:26.756
I hope.

08:26.839 --> 08:28.090
[rattling]

08:32.094 --> 08:33.596
[screams]

08:33.679 --> 08:36.515
{\an5}(Shout)
[gasps]
The Three Directions!

08:36.599 --> 08:38.142
What are you doing here?

08:38.226 --> 08:41.604
We hid in here after the concert
went all bonkers.

08:41.687 --> 08:43.606
And the ghost locked us in!

08:43.688 --> 08:45.191
I'd run if
I were you!

08:45.274 --> 08:47.443
{\an1}This place is
definitely haunted!

08:47.526 --> 08:48.194
Come on lads, let's go!

08:48.277 --> 08:51.948
[frightened yelping]

08:52.031 --> 08:55.910
{\an1}Bo Monkey and I are backstage
looking for ghosts.

08:55.993 --> 08:58.746
It's scary
because it's really dark.

08:58.829 --> 09:00.873
I can hear myself breathing

09:00.957 --> 09:03.209
because I'm breathing
very loudly.

09:03.292 --> 09:07.713
And I'm under this sheet,
and I can't see a thing,

09:07.797 --> 09:09.507
because I'm under the sheet.

09:11.717 --> 09:13.719
{\an1}[mumbling]

09:19.058 --> 09:22.103
[terrified mumbling]

09:22.937 --> 09:26.023
{\an1}[laughs]

09:26.107 --> 09:28.150
- [screams]
- Bo Monkey?

09:28.234 --> 09:28.818
Bo Monkey!

09:28.901 --> 09:30.653
[electronic beeping]

09:30.736 --> 09:32.321
Guys, come quick!

09:32.405 --> 09:34.365
My ghost detector
is going off!

09:34.448 --> 09:35.157
{\an1}Where?

09:35.241 --> 09:37.493
I don't see it!

09:37.576 --> 09:39.328
{\an3}Of course we don't.
It's a ghost!

09:39.412 --> 09:43.291
Some ghost-finding fog should
make the ghost visible.

09:43.374 --> 09:44.000
{\an3}Whoa.

09:44.083 --> 09:46.335
Okay, what's that?

09:47.920 --> 09:49.005
{\an1}Remember
what I said about

09:49.088 --> 09:50.464
{\an1}there's no such
thing as a ghost?

09:50.548 --> 09:52.591
Forget I ever said it.

09:52.675 --> 09:53.509
{\an1}Twist!

09:53.592 --> 09:55.344
{\an1}What!
Did you see a ghost?

09:55.428 --> 09:56.512
Bo thinks he saw one!

09:56.596 --> 09:57.471
{\an1}[coughs]

09:57.555 --> 09:58.806
It's kinda foggy in here.

09:58.889 --> 10:00.057
{\an3}Well this ghost detector
isn't working.

10:00.141 --> 10:04.979
Hey, you got that new ghost
finder fogger thing!

10:05.062 --> 10:06.314
It totally works great, huh?

10:06.397 --> 10:08.065
[hums guitar music]

10:08.149 --> 10:10.651
[gasping]

10:10.735 --> 10:12.028
This fog
makes me think

10:12.111 --> 10:14.030
you could write
an awesome song about fog!

10:14.113 --> 10:15.948
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

10:16.032 --> 10:19.368
♪ Fog on the wetlands ♪

10:19.452 --> 10:20.036
♪ Something something something
something in the sky ♪

10:20.119 --> 10:22.204
I love it!

10:22.288 --> 10:24.040
Oh my gosh. Oh my gosh.
Oh my gosh!

10:24.123 --> 10:25.541
{\an1}You're the Fresh
Beat Band!

10:25.625 --> 10:28.044
I'm Spooky Spooks.
Spooky for short.

10:28.127 --> 10:30.296
{\an1}What's up!

10:30.379 --> 10:32.715
Um, Hi there.

10:32.798 --> 10:34.050
Um, are you a ghost?

10:34.133 --> 10:36.802
{\an1}Yeah!

10:36.886 --> 10:37.803
{\an3}Yeah!

10:37.887 --> 10:38.220
Oh, well in that case...

10:38.304 --> 10:40.348
{\an1}[screams]

10:40.431 --> 10:42.767
{\an1}Oh, that's--
you're not that scary at all.

10:42.850 --> 10:44.727
I know!
Ghosts are just people.

10:44.810 --> 10:48.230
{\an3}See-through people,
but, you know, people.

10:48.314 --> 10:52.068
{\an1}But if you're a ghost,
how come we can see you now?

10:52.151 --> 10:53.861
{\an3}Oh, you can always
see me.

10:53.944 --> 10:57.365
{\an3}Except for when, you know,
I forget to make myself visible.

10:57.448 --> 10:58.699
And, Fresh Beat Band...

10:58.783 --> 11:02.912
{\an3}♪ You really know
how to rock ♪

11:02.995 --> 11:04.538
{\an3}Yeah!
[whistles]

11:04.622 --> 11:06.916
Here, Whispy!

11:06.999 --> 11:08.376
[mumbling]

11:08.459 --> 11:09.585
Your band rocks!

11:09.668 --> 11:11.587
{\an3}Whispy and I are
seriously, no joking,

11:11.670 --> 11:14.924
{\an3}ultra, mega fans
of yours!

11:15.007 --> 11:17.676
{\an1}I mean, if I could rock it
like you guys--

11:17.760 --> 11:24.225
it's my dream to be
the biggest rock star ever!

11:24.308 --> 11:26.852
Wow, thanks.

11:26.936 --> 11:30.106
But why are you trying to scare
everyone away from this theater?

11:30.189 --> 11:33.317
What? No, dude.
I love this place.

11:33.401 --> 11:33.901
{\an1}Sweet!

11:33.984 --> 11:35.986
{\an1}Oh!
[chuckles]

11:36.070 --> 11:40.449
{\an5}(Shout)
The thing is, Spooky,
every time someone plays here,

11:40.533 --> 11:41.909
you scare them away.

11:41.992 --> 11:45.538
{\an5}(Spooky)
Aw, man! I was afraid
that was because of me.

11:45.621 --> 11:46.956
I didn't mean to.

11:47.039 --> 11:50.793
I just want to be a part of it
so, so, so, so much.

11:50.876 --> 11:52.211
[mumbling, giggling]

11:52.294 --> 11:54.463
But everything always
goes kind of wonky.

11:54.547 --> 11:57.716
Like with the Three Directions.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.969
[cheering]

12:00.052 --> 12:01.595
(Spooky)
I was just gonna sing along,

12:01.679 --> 12:04.723
but I tripped over
a few things

12:04.807 --> 12:07.977
and then kinda accidentally
got one of the guys

12:08.060 --> 12:09.478
caught up in the mic cord.

12:09.562 --> 12:14.191
And then, um, yeah,
some other stuff.

12:15.151 --> 12:17.194
I just wanna rock.

12:17.278 --> 12:20.156
Aww, we understand, Spooky.

12:20.239 --> 12:22.491
You do?
I knew it!

12:22.575 --> 12:24.034
But if you keep
scaring everyone away,

12:24.118 --> 12:26.620
the theater will have
to close forever.

12:26.704 --> 12:27.538
[gasps]

12:27.621 --> 12:29.498
Close because of me?

12:29.582 --> 12:31.000
Oh, man.

12:31.083 --> 12:34.170
Maybe I should just
forget my dreams.

12:34.253 --> 12:36.505
No!
Don't give up, Spooky.

12:36.589 --> 12:40.384
If you have to rock,
you have to rock!

12:40.468 --> 12:43.345
Yeah, you just need to find
the band that's right for you.

12:43.429 --> 12:46.682
Yeah, and, you know,
find somewhere else to play.

12:46.765 --> 12:50.436
Dudes, when you are right,
you are right.

12:50.519 --> 12:51.520
Cool.

12:51.604 --> 12:52.188
I'm gonna go
figure this one out.

12:52.271 --> 12:54.398
Come on, Whispy!

12:54.482 --> 12:55.065
[mumbling]

12:55.149 --> 12:56.358
Thanks, Fresh Beat Band.

12:56.442 --> 12:58.527
See you later!

12:58.611 --> 12:59.778
- Spooky out!

12:59.862 --> 13:00.821
[guitar riff]

13:00.905 --> 13:03.157
- Bye!
- Bye, Spooky.

13:03.240 --> 13:04.450
Yeah, see ya!

13:04.533 --> 13:06.535
{\an3}Or, you know what
I mean.

13:06.619 --> 13:07.620
See through ya.

13:07.703 --> 13:10.539
[mumbling]

13:10.623 --> 13:11.916
[laughter]

13:11.999 --> 13:13.375
(Kiki)
Come on, guys.

13:13.459 --> 13:14.418
I know it was a late night
last night.

13:14.502 --> 13:16.712
Well, it was worth it.

13:16.795 --> 13:18.130
The theater's not going
to be closed,

13:18.214 --> 13:19.465
and we made a new friend.

13:19.548 --> 13:20.716
A ghost friend.

13:20.799 --> 13:22.718
I was pretty sure there was
a ghost in there.

13:22.801 --> 13:24.261
But we've got to rehearse for
our show at the amusement park.

13:24.345 --> 13:26.347
[snoring]

13:26.430 --> 13:26.847
Twist!

13:26.931 --> 13:28.599
[snoring]

13:28.682 --> 13:29.767
Huh?
Was--wasn't sleepin'.

13:29.850 --> 13:31.727
Brighter--wide awake.
Ready to rock!

13:31.810 --> 13:34.063
All right, let's do this!

13:34.146 --> 13:36.398
One, two, three, four!

13:36.482 --> 13:37.942
Yeah!
[guitar riff]

13:38.025 --> 13:39.360
Hey, Spooky!

13:39.443 --> 13:40.736
Hi!

13:40.819 --> 13:41.904
Guess what.

13:41.987 --> 13:43.239
I totally took your advice

13:43.322 --> 13:44.323
and found a band
that's perfect for me!

13:44.406 --> 13:46.742
Oh, you did?

13:46.825 --> 13:49.745
Who wants to rock
this practice, huh?

13:49.828 --> 13:50.955
Yeah!

13:51.038 --> 13:52.331
You guys!

13:52.831 --> 13:54.917
Oh, yeah!

13:55.000 --> 13:59.838
[humming]

13:59.922 --> 14:01.090
Great day!

14:01.173 --> 14:06.262
Uh, Spooky, um, see,
our band is already a band.

14:06.345 --> 14:08.180
A rockin' band!

14:08.264 --> 14:09.515
[guitar riff]

14:09.598 --> 14:10.516
[string snaps]

14:10.599 --> 14:11.725
[cymbal crash]

14:11.809 --> 14:12.726
[drum beat]

14:12.810 --> 14:14.520
[horn noises]

14:14.603 --> 14:17.314
Weird.
That's the sixth time this week.

14:17.398 --> 14:21.443
Anyway, you guys have totally
made my dream come true.

14:21.527 --> 14:23.612
I'm going to be
the rockin'-est, jammin'-est,

14:23.696 --> 14:27.116
freshest Fresh Beat ever!

14:27.199 --> 14:29.118
You are an amazing singer.

14:29.201 --> 14:31.537
And you do shred on the guitar.

14:31.620 --> 14:34.206
I guess you could sit in with us
for our practice.

14:34.290 --> 14:34.707
Would that be cool, guys?

14:34.790 --> 14:35.374
Um, sure!

14:35.457 --> 14:37.501
Yeah!

14:37.585 --> 14:38.627
Why not?

14:38.711 --> 14:41.463
{\an1}[mumbling]

14:41.547 --> 14:43.465
{\an3}[laughs]

14:43.549 --> 14:45.009
Yeah!

14:45.092 --> 14:50.055
Okay, for starters, here's one
I wrote based on true events.

14:50.139 --> 14:50.973
♪ Why you lookin' at me ♪

14:51.056 --> 14:52.725
♪ Like I'm not even there ♪

14:52.808 --> 14:55.144
♪ You're lookin' through me ♪

14:55.227 --> 14:56.145
♪ Like I'm made of air ♪

14:56.228 --> 14:58.314
Then Kiki does this sick
guitar riff

14:58.397 --> 15:00.649
[guitar riff]

15:00.733 --> 15:02.985
And then Marina starts
pulverizing those drums.

15:03.068 --> 15:06.447
[drum solo]

15:06.530 --> 15:08.699
[crash]

15:08.782 --> 15:10.075
Oh.

15:10.159 --> 15:11.327
Bongo head.
Bongo head.

15:11.410 --> 15:13.787
[grunting]

15:13.871 --> 15:15.247
[loud crash]

15:16.248 --> 15:19.251
[scatting]

15:21.170 --> 15:23.172
[grunting]

15:23.255 --> 15:26.300
[scatting]

15:26.717 --> 15:29.011
[crash]

15:29.094 --> 15:30.679
Oh, yikes!

15:30.763 --> 15:32.556
Did I do that?

15:35.768 --> 15:37.144
My next appointment
should be here soon.

15:37.227 --> 15:39.563
{\an3}Kiki, it is so cool
that you're so into hair,

15:39.647 --> 15:42.358
{\an3}because I am so, so,
really into hair.

15:42.441 --> 15:44.526
Wait.

15:44.610 --> 15:45.569
We should do
a song about hair!

15:45.653 --> 15:48.530
Something like, uh...

15:48.614 --> 15:50.866
♪ Long and flowing ♪

15:50.949 --> 15:52.701
♪ Soft and clean ♪

15:52.785 --> 15:57.164
♪ Hair is a growing
like I've never seen ♪

15:57.247 --> 15:58.290
Spooky!
[chuckles]

15:58.374 --> 15:59.249
That sounds great,

15:59.333 --> 16:01.752
but I have some
hair appointments.

16:01.835 --> 16:04.713
Would you mind
not being so visible?

16:04.797 --> 16:06.465
Totally get it!

16:06.548 --> 16:08.384
Not even a little prob.

16:10.427 --> 16:11.887
Welcome, everyone.

16:11.970 --> 16:13.514
Take a seat, and I'll
get to you as soon as I can.

16:13.597 --> 16:17.184
Okay, we'll do a quick trim
and conditioning treatment.

16:17.267 --> 16:18.727
{\an1}So, how long
you think you'll be?

16:18.811 --> 16:20.979
{\an3}Um, we're just
getting started here.

16:21.063 --> 16:23.399
Get it. Got it.
Filed it away.

16:23.482 --> 16:24.608
{\an1}Did you ask me
something, Kiki?

16:24.692 --> 16:26.318
{\an3}Oh, no.

16:26.402 --> 16:29.071
Ooh, I know what I can do:

16:29.154 --> 16:30.406
help get these do's done,

16:30.489 --> 16:33.742
so we can
get to our show on time.

16:33.826 --> 16:36.453
Well, what do you think, Kiki?

16:36.537 --> 16:38.414
Oh, no.

16:38.497 --> 16:40.249
Spooky in the house!

16:40.332 --> 16:41.333
[gasping]

16:41.417 --> 16:44.503
[screaming]

16:44.586 --> 16:46.171
No! Everybody, please.

16:46.255 --> 16:47.965
I can explain!

16:48.048 --> 16:48.924
[sighs]

16:49.007 --> 16:51.135
{\an1}Sorry, Kik-ster.
Just trying to help.

16:51.218 --> 16:52.511
[cheering]

16:52.594 --> 16:54.221
[upbeat rock music]

16:54.304 --> 16:55.431
Check it out!

16:55.514 --> 16:57.349
This is so huge, you guys.

16:57.433 --> 16:58.267
My first real live gig!

16:58.350 --> 17:00.436
{\an3}Yeah.

17:00.519 --> 17:02.104
{\an3}Why don't you
keep practicing,

17:02.187 --> 17:05.022
{\an3}and we're just going to go talk
about the show for a second.

17:05.107 --> 17:06.275
{\an1}Cool, man.

17:06.358 --> 17:07.901
{\an1}I got a couple moves
to learn.

17:10.194 --> 17:12.781
Guys, I've got a bad feeling.

17:12.865 --> 17:16.117
Yeah, I'm worried Spooky might
scare away the audience too.

17:16.201 --> 17:17.869
No, I mean I sat on a banana.

17:17.953 --> 17:20.955
But it's her dream, guys.

17:21.039 --> 17:23.000
{\an1}I mean, what's the worst
that could happen?

17:23.083 --> 17:26.920
{\an5}(Spooky)
Guys, I'm going to head out
there and set the instruments.

17:27.003 --> 17:28.255
Spooky, no!

17:28.338 --> 17:32.217
[cheering]

17:32.301 --> 17:34.845
That.
That could happen.

17:34.928 --> 17:36.013
[groans]

17:36.096 --> 17:37.139
All right, then.
Places!

17:37.222 --> 17:38.557
Curtain up!

17:38.640 --> 17:40.476
(Spooky)
Check, one, two, three!

17:40.559 --> 17:41.643
Are you guys ready to rock!

17:41.727 --> 17:44.480
[cheering]

17:44.563 --> 17:47.691
(Spooky)
Then give it up for Spooky!

17:47.775 --> 17:50.486
And the Fresh Beats!

17:50.569 --> 17:51.904
Wait, that's us!

17:51.987 --> 17:55.157
Well, Spooky and us.

17:55.240 --> 17:56.533
Whoa!

17:58.202 --> 18:01.830
♪ ♪

18:01.914 --> 18:03.081
Whoa!

18:03.165 --> 18:05.959
♪ ♪

18:06.043 --> 18:09.505
♪ I've been looking for a friend
like you ♪

18:09.588 --> 18:13.842
♪ Someone to make each day
brand-new ♪

18:13.926 --> 18:16.428
♪ And share the sun,
yeah this blue sky too ♪

18:16.512 --> 18:18.889
Okay!

18:18.972 --> 18:22.726
♪ I've been looking for a friend
like you ♪

18:22.810 --> 18:23.769
♪ I've been looking for a friend
like you ♪

18:23.852 --> 18:26.355
What's going on here?

18:26.438 --> 18:29.566
{\an1}I don't know,
but it's kinda spooky.

18:29.650 --> 18:34.363
Whoo! All right!
Oh, no!

18:34.446 --> 18:35.614
Sorry! Mic slipped.

18:35.697 --> 18:36.698
[screams]

18:36.782 --> 18:39.535
It's a ghost!

18:39.618 --> 18:40.828
[screaming]

18:40.911 --> 18:43.413
Wait!
Don't go!

18:43.497 --> 18:44.832
Aw, man!

18:44.915 --> 18:46.542
You guys, we were rockin'!

18:46.625 --> 18:50.212
Uh, Spooky...

18:50.295 --> 18:51.672
It happened again.

18:51.755 --> 18:54.508
This is all my fault.

18:54.591 --> 18:56.510
I ruined your gig.

18:56.593 --> 18:57.553
I can never be a rock star.

18:57.636 --> 18:59.513
Aww, Spooky.

18:59.596 --> 19:00.806
Sorry, guys.

19:00.889 --> 19:02.307
I'm out of the band.

19:02.391 --> 19:06.061
You're great, but I'm just
messing it all up.

19:06.144 --> 19:08.689
Come on, Whispy.
Let's get out of here.

19:08.772 --> 19:11.108
Spooky out.

19:11.191 --> 19:12.985
[sad mumbling]

19:17.155 --> 19:17.781
{\an3}[mumbling]

19:17.865 --> 19:20.617
Aww, it's okay buddy.

19:20.701 --> 19:23.787
Have a squashed banana.

19:23.871 --> 19:26.874
{\an3}[crying]

19:30.252 --> 19:32.796
Aww, poor Spooky.

19:32.880 --> 19:35.674
She shouldn't have to give up
on her dream just like that.

19:35.757 --> 19:37.217
{\an3}There's gotta be something
we can do to help her.

19:41.388 --> 19:43.557
[mumbling]

19:43.640 --> 19:46.018
If only there were
some place she could sing.

19:46.101 --> 19:49.104
Some place where
she won't scare everyone away.

19:49.187 --> 19:50.397
[screams]

19:50.480 --> 19:51.106
A ghost!

19:51.189 --> 19:53.400
[all gasp]
Spooky!

19:53.483 --> 19:54.151
{\an3}[laughs]

19:54.234 --> 19:57.362
Oh, that scared me so bad.

19:57.446 --> 19:58.614
{\an1}[laughs]

19:58.697 --> 20:01.617
{\an1}Yeah, all that crazy floating
stuff was amazing!

20:01.700 --> 20:03.827
Excuse me.

20:03.911 --> 20:05.579
You saw a ghost,
and you're laughing?

20:05.662 --> 20:06.788
Well, sure.

20:06.872 --> 20:08.999
{\an1}Getting scared's what makes
a haunted house fun.

20:09.082 --> 20:12.336
[laughs]
That was so cool!

20:12.419 --> 20:13.629
Brainstorm!

20:13.712 --> 20:14.755
People like being scared
when they expect it!

20:14.838 --> 20:17.466
Yeah, like Halloween.

20:17.549 --> 20:19.092
Or at a scary movie.

20:19.176 --> 20:22.638
Yeah, people like being scared
when they expect to be scared.

20:22.721 --> 20:23.931
That's why they go to a...

20:24.014 --> 20:25.682
(all)
Haunted house!

20:25.766 --> 20:29.978
{\an5}(Marina)
Calling this "The Haunted House
of Rock" was a great idea!

20:30.062 --> 20:31.813
Come on!
It's almost show time.

20:31.897 --> 20:35.525
{\an1}Guys, I just want to say how
much this means to me.

20:35.609 --> 20:37.110
{\an1}I really think
we're gonna rock it!

20:37.194 --> 20:40.072
Everyone got your gadgets ready?

20:41.615 --> 20:43.533
All set.

20:43.617 --> 20:44.576
One, two, three, four.

20:44.660 --> 20:48.288
[cheering]

20:48.372 --> 20:49.414
Let's rock it!

20:49.498 --> 20:51.041
♪ ♪

20:51.124 --> 20:54.169
♪ Play it loud,
just like a rock star ♪

20:54.252 --> 20:56.421
♪ Shout it out,
just like a rock star ♪

20:56.505 --> 21:00.092
♪ Come on everybody,
let me hear you say ♪

21:00.175 --> 21:03.428
♪ You feel just like a rock
star, hey, hey ♪

21:03.512 --> 21:03.845
♪ Here we go now ♪

21:03.929 --> 21:06.515
♪ ♪

21:06.598 --> 21:07.599
Yeah!

21:07.683 --> 21:08.684
♪ ♪

21:08.767 --> 21:10.185
Sing it, Shout!

21:10.269 --> 21:12.688
♪ You know the fun never ends ♪

21:12.771 --> 21:14.189
♪ The fun never ends ♪

21:14.272 --> 21:15.691
♪ When you and all
of your friends ♪

21:15.774 --> 21:18.151
That's right!

21:18.235 --> 21:20.404
♪ Are rockin' out
in an awesome band ♪

21:20.487 --> 21:23.782
♪ Everybody's jammin',
so give us a hand ♪

21:23.865 --> 21:27.494
♪ Put your rock star jacket on ♪

21:27.577 --> 21:30.372
♪ Everybody play along ♪

21:30.455 --> 21:33.458
♪ Let's help each other,
let's give it a spin ♪

21:33.542 --> 21:37.879
♪ 'Cause if the music's bumpin',
everyone wins ♪

21:37.963 --> 21:40.340
♪ Play it loud
just like a rock star ♪

21:40.424 --> 21:43.385
♪ Shout it out
just like a rock star ♪

21:43.468 --> 21:46.388
♪ Come on everybody
let me here you say ♪

21:46.471 --> 21:50.225
♪ I feel just like a rock star,
hey, hey, hey ♪

21:50.308 --> 21:51.560
That's right.

21:51.643 --> 21:54.146
♪ Just like a rock star,
hey, hey hey ♪

21:54.229 --> 21:55.230
Yeah!

21:55.313 --> 21:57.399
Spooky in the house!

21:57.482 --> 21:59.860
Thank you!
Thank you!

21:59.943 --> 22:00.944
Guys, that was a great show.

22:01.028 --> 22:04.281
What a great adventure!

22:04.364 --> 22:05.741
What a great mission!

22:05.824 --> 22:07.117
What a great day.

22:09.036 --> 22:09.953
(Fresh Beat Band)
♪ We had a great day ♪

22:10.037 --> 22:13.123
♪ It was a super way ♪

22:13.206 --> 22:17.669
♪ To spend some time together ♪

22:17.753 --> 22:20.756
♪ La, la-la-la-la-la ♪

22:20.839 --> 22:22.382
♪ Hey ♪

22:22.466 --> 22:23.550
♪ Great day ♪

22:23.633 --> 22:24.801
♪ A great, great day ♪

22:24.885 --> 22:25.761
♪ Oh, yeah ♪

22:25.844 --> 22:27.012
♪ Great day ♪

22:27.095 --> 22:28.930
♪ And it goes a little
something like this ♪

22:29.014 --> 22:30.348
♪ Oh, yeah! ♪
